I '''Salman Amin 'Sal' Khan''' ({{lang-bn|সালমান খান}};<ref>{{cite video |people=Salman Khan |year=2011 |title=Understanding South Indian Naming |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Zf_PFN-kbg |medium=YouTube |language=English |publisher= khanacademy |accessdate=2012-6-30 }}</ref> mibait 1976) edukador yang Bangladeshi American ampong a talatátag king [[Khan Academy]], metung a libring platform king [[Aptas]] (''online'') king pamanuru ampong aguman a e pangtubu (''nonprofit''). Manibat king metung a malating upisina king bale na, mekalalang neng  atlung libung (3000) video o alben a magpalino kareng paksang [[academiku]], keraklan king  [[matematika]] ampong [[syensya]]. Anyang Julio 2012, miras nong 355,000 deng ''subscriber'' o talataluki ning Khan Academy channel king YouTube.<ref>{{cite web|title=khanacademy's YouTube Channel|url=http://www.youtube.com/user/khanacademy}}</ref> Anyang 2012, pinili ne ning magasin a Americanung ''[[Time (magasin)|Time]]'' i Salman Khan ketang kayang banwa-banwang listahan da reng dinalan a maimpluwensiyang diling tau king yatu (''100 most influential people in the world''):  [[Time 100]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Salman Khan - Time 100|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111942,00.html|accessdate=22 April 2012|newspaper=[[Time (magazine){{!}}Time]]|date=18 April 2012}}</ref>

